d5d9f1f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/54/The_First_Purge_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F54%2FThe_First_Purge_Poster.jpg&h=1b9db132&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/70/The_Purge_Election_Year_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F70%2FThe_Purge_Election_Year_Poster.jpg&h=86e08f60&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/2/29/The_Purge_%E2%80%93_Anarchy_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F2%2F29%2FThe_Purge_%25E2%2580%2593_Anarchy_Poster.jpg&h=866b0a97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.電影改編自蒂姆詹金(Tim Jenkin)的2003年的自傳《Inside Out: Escape from Pretoria Prison》（新版本，原版在1987年在倫敦即有出版），描述1978的南非尚處於種族隔離政策中，Tim Jenkin與Stephen Lee兩位白人因為對抗種族隔離政策而被視作恐怖份子，分別被判處12年與8年刑期，關在比勒陀利亞中央監獄(Pretoria Central Prison)，兩人試著逃脫的故事。<br />\n<br />\n2.為了將當今的犯罪率降低至1%以下，執政黨「美國新建國元勳」（New Founding Fathers of America，簡稱NFFA）開始進行了一項社會測驗，並於晚間在一個孤立的社區中執行測試。但當壓迫者的暴力引發了群眾的憤怒時，該活動從社區的邊界開始蔓延至全國，名為「國定殺戮日」<br />\n<br />\n3.2022年，殺戮日開始的兩小時前，商人詹姆士&middot;桑丁在自己的家庭保全裝置而使自己公司銷售額大獲全勝，於是開心地回到自己家向妻子瑪麗、女兒佐伊與兒子查理宣布了好消息，隨後與家人等待殺戮夜晚的來臨。兩小時後，殺戮日開始的一分鐘前，詹姆士野心勃勃地為家人展示了自己引以為豪的堡壘型保全系統：利用幾英尺高的淬火鋼封住所有的窗戶與大門..<br />\n<br />\n4.2023年，在洛杉磯市區中，警察中士李歐&middot;巴恩斯在全副武裝、身穿防彈衣、不顧自己前妻的警告而開著一輛加固警車，打算利用這場夜晚去殺一個他最憎恨的人。夜幕降臨，全國開始播報預警系統，洛杉磯也隨之展開了了長達十二小時的大屠殺，虎視眈眈的人們開始手持武器、大呼痛快地走到街道上獵殺。...<br />\n<br />\n5.<img src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/jj-6p5Qw_kFMtcVFEDaoLgeLhBs=/0x0:1000x800/1200x800/filters:focal(424x146:584x306)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/66498759/hunt2.0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fthumbor%2Fjj-6p5Qw_kFMtcVFEDaoLgeLhBs%3D%2F0x0%3A1000x800%2F1200x800%2Ffilters%3Afocal%28424x146%3A584x306%29%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fuploads%2Fchorus_image%2Fimage%2F66498759%2Fhunt2.0.jpg&h=7574f209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5 50PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=50fc53f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=e6c5294c\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de2f9b649a0bafeefc8da6fb309109584090ddf2","tid":1935041,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T09:49:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300f684de946bfa89bd4bab164cc7c6cd2eeb24b","tid":1935041,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T10:26:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"073b0639b826766eb2294ebff6a960d8a6aed50e","tid":1935041,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T11:06:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e779e62973ab022679960fa7a016b69dbb5a9d","tid":1935041,"uid":29160,"like":0,"